-- Jefferies Hires Peter Bacchus to Run European Investment Bank, Times Says
-- B y   B e n   F a r e y
-- 2010-12-12T08:48:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-12/jefferies-hires-head-of-european-banking-arm-sunday-times-says.html
Jefferies Group Inc . hired  Peter Bacchus , 41, to head its European investment banking arm, in a
newly created role, the  Sunday Times  reported, without saying
where it got the information.  Bacchus resigned as global head of mining at Morgan Stanley
on Dec. 10, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Farey in London at 
